cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with spatiotemporal representations of videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves a recurrent neural network, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on a large-scale dataset, which is a common aspect of multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the use of fewer parameters is a common goal in neural network optimization, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
